channel.title: How to fix Skillcape shop crash (InsidiaX)
channel.description:
[size=18pt]Ok first off this is probably the easiest tutorial It's client sided so go to your Client And go to[/size]:[size=18pt]ItemDef.Java[/size] Find: [totalItems + 5000]
Change 5000 to 50000
And your done Im not sure if there a crash like this for any other Client but i had this same problem and fixed that's all! :D
